<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
      <hr>

      <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "Matthew.jpg", width: 200, alt: 'profile-pic', class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>A full stack engineer with experience in Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, and Python  technologies to build an exceptional online presence. Eager to learn new languages, frameworks, and to take on challenges in constant desire of a results-oriented atmosphere. Astute ability in JavaScript for client and server side scripting (React/Redux/NodeJS) and always researching and studying new languages that are effective in modern culture. Works extremely well in team oriented settings and has copious amounts of enthusiasm to code.</p>

        <p>Always seeking new opportunities and striving for the best. My best work is ahead of me and I hope that I can contribute my skills and knowledge to any company that is willing and happy to have me. </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='jobHistory'
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='education'
          >
            Education
          </button>

        </p>
        <p>

          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <p class="card-detail">
                <span class="title">Cisco</span> - 
                <span class="role">Software Engineer/DevOps</span> -
                <span class="tech">React/Redux/Python/Django/REST</span>
              </p>
              <p class="card-detail">Feb 2018 - May 2018</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <p class="card-detail">
                <span class="title">TiVo</span> - 
                <span class="role">Software Engineer</span> -
                <span class="tech">Drupal/Salesforce/jQuery</span>
              </p>
              <p class="card-detail">Aug 2016 - Jun 2017</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <p class="card-detail">
                <span class="title">Impressions</span> - 
                <span class="role">Software Engineer</span> -
                <span class="tech">React/Node.JS</span>
              </p>
              <p class="card-detail">Apr 2016 - Jun 2016</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <p class="card-detail">
                <span class="title">University of California, Santa Cruz</span> - 
                <span class="role">Molecular and Celluar Biology</span> 
              </p>
              <p class="card-detail">Aug 2009 - Jun 2012</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>

